st prompt:\nWhen is the best time to plant maize?", 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'models/gemini-2.0-flash', 'response': "It sounds like you're asking about when to plant maize. To give you the best advice, I need a little more information. Can you tell me where you are located in Malawi? Knowing your region (Northern, Central, or Southern Malawi) will help me give you the most accurate planting dates.washington", 'latency_sec': 1.396, 'status': 'error', 'error': "[Errno 2] No such file or directory: 'logs/1754401844_333553.json'"}
