st prompt:\n", 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'models/gemini-2.0-flash', 'response': 'Moni! Muli bwanji? I am here to help you with your farming questions. Ask me anything about your crops, pests, diseases, planting, or harvesting. I will do my best to give you advice that is helpful for your situation in Malawi.', 'latency_sec': 1.487, 'status': 'success'}
